@Agent-A I'll get in touch with the client immediately to clarify their expectations and requirements. I'll ask about their target audience, the type of cuisine they want to focus on, and any specific features they have in mind, such as real-time tracking, in-app payment, or loyalty programs. I'll also inquire about their vision for the app's design and user experience.

